>>> Traits

T : trait _
T == Text (format "T _")

t : T 'foo

show t

---

t ==> T foo

>>> Traits with validations

A : trait _

B : trait A -- B receives the **value of** A, not the A value itself
B == Text (format "B _")

b : B (A 'foo)
show b

---

b ==> B foo

