>>> Conformances

A : trait _
Name n == A n
A == Text (format "A _")

B : trait _
A a == B a
B == Text (format "B _")

show (A for 'foo)
show (B for A for 'foo)

---

(A for 'foo) ==> A foo
(B for A for 'foo) ==> B foo
